quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  52,1,"M wẽen ne Tʋʋre (yaa tãng yʋʋre)."
  52,2,"La ne gaf sẽn maneg n gʋlse."
  52,3,"N be bũn-gʋlsdg pʋg n yadge!"
  52,4,"La ne Roogã Mɑlεk-rãmbã sẽn gũm-ɑ sɑɑsẽ wã, tɩ yɑɑ Wẽnd tũudum."
  52,5,"Lɑ M wẽen ne Sɑɑgã sẽn zẽkã n yɑɑ beengã."
  52,6,"Lɑ ne mogrã sẽn dems ne koomɑ."
  52,7,"Ad fo Soabã namsgã na n yɩɩme."
  52,8,"A pa tar tusd ye."
  52,9,"Raar ning saagã sẽn na n leng n dãmb rãmbg tεkẽ"
  52,10,"Tɩ tãmsã na n kẽn ne kẽna."
  52,11,"Rẽn Wɩɩbd be ra-kãng raarã ne yagsdbã."
  52,12,"Neb nins sẽn be-b faoob pʋgẽ n wɩsdã."
  52,13,"Raar ning b sẽn tusd-b n tʋgd Gεhannam bugmẽ wã ne pãnga."
  52,14,"Yãoondã la Bugum ning yãmb sẽn da yɩ n yagsdẽ wã."
  52,15,"Yaa tɩɩm la woto bɩ, bɩ yãmb pa ne-ɑ?"
  52,16,"Kẽ-y-yã-a. Y maanda sugri, y pa maand sugri, fãa yaa yembr yãmb zugu. Ad b sẽn rol yãmbã yaa y sẽn da tʋmdɑ keoore."
  52,17,"Ad wẽn-zoεtbã bee Arzãn-dãmb pʋgẽ la neema."
  52,18,"N wʋmd noog ne bũmb ning b Soabã sẽn kõ-ba, la b Soabã gũ-b ne Gεhɩɩm Bugmã."
  52,19,"Rɩ-y la y yũ; yaa beelg ne yãmb sẽn da yɩ n tʋmdẽ wã."
  52,20,"Bãmb yaa sẽn kɩll gãas sẽn tedg zugu, la b loe b fur ne Hʋʋr-aeen-rãmba."
  52,21,"La neb nins sẽn kõ sɩda, tɩ b koambã me pʋg-b ne Liimaoongo, b paamsda bãmb ne b koambã. Tõnd pa mongd b tʋʋmẽ wã baa fʋɩ, ned fãa yaa sẽn gãneg ne a sẽn tʋm bũmb ningã wã."
  52,22,"La D paas-b tɩ-biis la nemd b sẽn maan nonglem."
  52,23,"B tata taab a pʋgẽ ko-teese, gom-zaal pa be a pʋgẽ, beegr yell me pa be a pʋgẽ."
  52,24,"La gilgda b zugu, koamb-bãɑngo tɩ yɑɑ bãmb sõgneg yĩngɑ, b yaa wa Lʋʋlʋʋ(koom n sãnem) sẽn solge n be ɑ wʋʋgẽ."
  52,25,"Tɩ b sãnda togl sãnda n sogsd taaba."
  52,26,"N yetẽ: ""ad tõnd ra yɩɩme n be d nebẽ wã n yaeesdẽ, wãndã taoore."
  52,27,"Tɩ Wẽnd maan tõnd neema la A gũ tõnd n yi Samuum naongã (naon-zẽndga)."
  52,28,"Tõnd da yɩɩme n pĩnd n kot-A. Ad Yẽnda, Yẽ la manegda, Yẽ la Yoalsda."
  52,29,"Bɩ f tẽege; ne f Soabã neema, (Alkʋrãɑnɑ), tɩ fo pa yɩ ne neemã wã sɑbɑbo n yaa bag-bʋgd ye, f pa gãeeng me."
  52,30,"Bɩ b yetame tɩ yaa yɩɩl-yɩɩnda tɩ d koalld-a ne zamaan yel-soald ɑ kũum wɑ rɩkɑ, tɩ d pɑɑm d mengɑ."
  52,31,"Yeele: koll-y-yã-a, tɩ ad ma me lagma yãmb n yaa koallda."
  52,32,"Bɩ bãmb yam rãmbã n sagend-b ne woto, bɩ bãmb yaa neb sẽn yaa kεdgba?"
  52,33,"Bɩ b yetame: ""a pasa zĩri?"". Pa woto ye! B pa kõt sɩd ye."
  52,34,"Bɩ b wa ne gomd sẽn wõnd-a tɩ b sã n yaa sɩd rãmba."
  52,35,"Bɩ b naana bãmb ne zaalem, bɩ yaa bãmb la naandbã?"
  52,36,"Bɩ bãmb n naan saasã la Tẽngã? Pa woto ye! B pa bãng n wãag ye."
  52,37,"Bɩ fo Soabã sãnem baoã bee bãmb nengẽ, bɩ yaa bãmb la windbã."
  52,38,"Bɩ bãmb tara raodg n kεlgd a pʋgẽ, bɩ b kelgdã wa ne tagmas sẽn yaa vẽenega."
  52,39,"Bɩ Yẽ n tar kom-pugli tɩ yãmb n tar kom-ribli?"
  52,40,"Bɩ fo sokd-b-la keoore, tɩ bãmb be samd pʋgẽ tɩ zɩsg b zugu?"
  52,41,"Bɩ bãmb tara sẽn solge, tɩ bãmb gʋlsdẽ?"
  52,42,"Bɩ yaa rabs-wẽng la b rata? Rẽnd neb nins sẽn kɩfl-bã, bãmb bɑl la b sẽn rabs rab-wẽnga."
  52,43,"Bɩ bãmb tara soab sẽn pa Wẽnde? Wẽnd yɩlgame n yi bũmb ning bãmb sẽn maan lagem-n-taarã."
  52,44,"La b sã n yã gɩrg sẽn yi saasẽ wã n yaa sẽn lʋɩtẽ la b sẽn yete: ""yaa sawat gũmdi""."
  52,45,"Bɩ f bas-b hal tɩ b wa sεg b raar ning b sẽn na n gõgsd a pʋgẽ (tɩ yaa wala saag n wẽ-ba)."
  52,46,"Raar ning bãmb rabrã sẽn ka nafd-b n yi ba fʋɩ; bãmb me, b pa na n sõng-ba."
  52,47,"La be ne sẽn wẽgd-bã, naong sẽn pa rẽnda; la ad b wʋsg fãa pa mi ye."
  52,48,"La f maan sugr ne fo Soabã bʋʋdã, tɩ fo bee Tõnd nenem pʋga. La f yɩlg ne fo Soabã pẽgr wakat ning fo sẽn wat n yiki."
  52,49,"La yʋngã, bɩ f yɩlg-A, la ãdsã kõom wakato."
